  "texts": [
    "In the case that we do not use feedforward, in addition to obtaining the correct outcome for the W measurement, we must also post-select on obtaining the correct outcome of the initial measurement of S Z.",
    "We obtain the +1 eigenvalue subspace of this operator with probability 1/2.",
    "We, therefore, have Q PS = 3/4 × 1/2 = 3/8.",
    "Finally, in the standard preparation procedure, we measure both S Z and S X, and we require that both give the +1 outcome.",
    "Each measurement gives the correct outcome with probability 1/2."
  ],
